za.co.logoinstructor.processor
Class InstructionSetProcessor

java.lang.Object
  za.co.logoinstructor.processor.InstructionSetProcessor

public class InstructionSetProcessor
extends java.lang.Object

The InstructionSetProcessor will do some basic validation on the instruction set XML file.
It will request the XML JAXB objects from @see InstructionSetXMLProcessor.
It will provide some basic info about the instruction set and pass the command for each command to @see InstructionSetActionExecutor.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Romeo Dickason
